at a decreasing Lyman alpha escape\nfraction with increasing UV galaxy luminosity is a key element in our model to\nexplain the of larger xLya fractions for fainter LBGs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Sep 2011 16:14:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
