 to be at least $2n+1$ if Breaker is only allowed to use a pairing\nstrategy, thus the main term of our bound is optimal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Sep 2011 21:00:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-03-08"}
