ons to the following\nspectral lines are also presented: CaII H and K, MgII h and k, NaI D1 and D2,\nthe BaII 4554A and 4934A resonance lines, the CrI triplet at 5207A, the OI\ntriplet at 7773A, the MgI b-lines, and the H-alpha and Ly-alpha lines of HI.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Sep 2011 12:18:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
